@startuml 1F_Platform_Plan_Billing
title 1-F · Platform Plan & Billing Management (UC-P10 to UC-P13)

start
|Service Admin (Super Admin/Billing Admin)|
:Log in to Platform Admin;
:Open Plan & Billing Management;

if (Admin action?) then (Create Plan)
  :Enter plan name, price, billing cycle,\nfeature limits and active flag;
  |System|
  :Validate plan data;
  if (Plan valid?) then (No)
    :Return 422 validation error;
    stop
  else (Yes)
    :Create Plan record;
    :Write audit log;
  endif
elseif (Admin action?) then (Assign Plan to Tenant)
  :Select tenant and active plan;
  |System|
  :Check MANAGE_PLANS permission;
  :Validate tenant ACTIVE and plan active;
  if (Assignment allowed?) then (No)
    :Return 422/403 error;
    stop
  else (Yes)
    :Store previous plan for rollback;
    :Update TenantSubscription.plan_id;
    :Refresh tenant feature entitlement;
    :Write audit log;
  endif
elseif (Admin action?) then (Change Tenant Plan)
  :Select target tenant subscription and new plan;
  |System|
  :Run PlanEligibilityPolicy;
  :Update subscription and billing metadata;
  :Write audit log;
else (View Platform Invoices)
  |System|
  :Load platform invoices by tenant,\nstatus, date and provider reference;
  |Service Admin (Super Admin/Billing Admin)|
  :Filter, view invoice detail or export list;
endif

stop
@enduml
